ABOUT STL 

stl is a set of c++ function/classes to perform varous tasks. 

there is a wide varitey of fucntion and classes for different appplications 

stl objects are more efficient, bug-free and easier to used than custom impleentations 

----
1.Pair 

pairs are useful when dealing with two realted values. For example. For example, storing a range [L,R]

Pairs have inbuilt comparators such <,> etc 

Usage : 

pair<int, int > ={1,2}

